subject: p16751749
Findings: Per chest x-ray small right apical pneumothorax is present. This area can now no longer be evaluated due to overlying subcutaneous emphysema. Few opacifications have been present on numerous previous films. There is an increased density around the right chest tube which was not present on the chest x-ray of though was present on the prior chest x-ray of 4:00 am. This is thought to probably represent atelectasis but could represent an area of infection.
